    <h1 class="display-3">E-Project Archive API Documentation</h1>
    
  </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <p class="mt-4">Base URL: <code>http://localhost:3000</code></p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">User Registration</h2>
    <p>Register a new user with a username and password.</p>
    <code>POST /api/register</code>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>username</strong> (string) - The username for the new user.</li>
        <li><strong>password</strong> (string) - The password for the new user.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">User Login</h2>
    <p>Authenticate a user with their username and password.</p>
    <code>POST /api/login</code>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>username</strong> (string) - The username of the user.</li>
        <li><strong>password</strong> (string) - The password of the user.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">Search Project</h2>
    <p>Search for a project by a keyword.</p>
    <code>POST /api/search-project</code>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>keyword</strong> (string) - The keyword to search for in project names or descriptions.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">Upload Project</h2>
    <p>Upload a new project with a name, description, and a file.</p>
    <code>POST /api/upload-project</code>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>projectName</strong> (string) - The name of the project.</li>
        <li><strong>projectDescription</strong> (string) - The description of the project.</li>
        <li><strong>projectFile</strong> (file) - The project file to upload.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">Edit Project</h2>
    <p>Edit an existing project by its ID.</p>
    <code>PUT /api/edit-project/:id</code>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>id</strong> (string) - The ID of the project to edit.</li>
        <li><strong>projectName</strong> (string) - The updated name of the project.</li>
        <li><strong>projectDescription</strong> (string) - The updated description of the project.</li>
        <li><strong>projectFile</strong> (file) - The project file to upload.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">Delete Project</h2>
    <p>Delete an existing project by its ID.</p>
    <code>DELETE /api/delete-project/:id</code>
    
